slpkg: slpkg (Slackware Packaging Tool)
slpkg:
slpkg: Slpkg is a feature-rich package manager for Slackware-based systems.
slpkg: It installs, upgrades, removes, and builds packages from multiple
slpkg: repositories, including SlackBuilds.org (SBo, Ponce) and binary
slpkg: repositories. Slpkg automatically resolves and tracks dependencies,
slpkg: maintains a full installation history with transaction rollback,
slpkg: detects orphaned and foreign packages, and verifies the integrity
slpkg: of installed files.
